tePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 14:25:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/space-in-the-seventies-a-spacecrafts-second-life-part-2</guid></item><item><title>阿瑟·C·克拉克的心灵超越</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/arthur-c-clarkes-transcendence-of-mind</link><description>《太空漫游》系列如何将猿类、宇航员、人工智能和外星机器转变为提升、人工智能对齐失败、人机合并和独立于基质的思维的阶段性愿景。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/arthur-c-clarkes-transcendence-of-mind.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 14:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/arthur-c-clarkes-transcendence-of-mind</guid></item><item><title>为什么网络安全对美国的人工智能领导地位很重要</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/why-cybersecurity-matters-for-americas-ai-leadership</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 13:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/why-cybersecurity-matters-for-americas-ai-leadership</guid></item><item><title>大脑的语言网络比之前想象的更广泛</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-brains-language-network-is-more-extensive-than-previously-thought</link><description>几十年来，神经科学家已经知道大脑左半球的特定区域负责处理语言。然而，麻省理工学院研究人员的一项新研究表明，语言处理也发生在大脑的许多其他部分。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-brains-language-network-is-more-extensive-than-previously-thought.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 13:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-brains-language-network-is-more-extensive-than-previously-thought</guid></item><item><title>新的 4D 打印方法可制造更轻、旋转速度更快的风力涡轮机叶片</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-4d-printing-method-creates-lighter-faster-spinning-wind-turbine-blades</link><description>康考迪亚研究人员开发的一种新制造技术可以使小型风力涡轮机更轻、更便宜且更容易生产。使用复合材料 4D 打印工艺，博士。候选人 Emad Fakhimi 和 Concordia 复合材料中心教授 Suong Van Hoa 用扁平碳纤维复合材料板制造了垂直轴风力涡轮机的弯曲叶片。该研究是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-4d-printing-method-creates-lighter-faster-spinning-wind-turbine-blades2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 13:25:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-4d-printing-method-creates-lighter-faster-spinning-wind-turbine-blades</guid></item><item><title>令人惊叹的照片揭示了真菌错综复杂的美丽</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/stunning-photos-reveal-the-intricate-beauty-of-fungi</link><description>这些图像记录了新西兰真菌和粘菌的鲜艳色彩和精致细节，取自 Jay Lichter 的新书&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/stunning-photos-reveal-the-intricate-beauty-of-fungi.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 13:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/stunning-photos-reveal-the-intricate-beauty-of-fungi</guid></item><item><title>受大脑启发的人工智能架构可以计算速度更快且耗电更少</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/brain-inspired-ai-architecture-could-computing-faster-and-far-less-power-hungry</link><description>尖峰神经网络 (SNN) 是一种人工智能 (AI) 模型，其灵感来自生物神经元如何相互通信。生物神经元以电脉冲的形式交换信息，而 SNN 则依赖于称为尖峰的短暂信号。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/brain-inspired-ai-architecture-could-computing-faster-and-far-less-power-hungry3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 12:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/brain-inspired-ai-architecture-could-computing-faster-and-far-less-power-hungry</guid></item><item><title>磷脂酶 B (LOC_Os11g43510) 的基因组编辑可促进米糠三酰甘油稳定性而不影响种子萌发</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/genome-editing-of-phospholipase-b-loc_os11g43510-promotes-rice-bran-triacylglycerol-stability-without-affecting-seed-germination</link><description>磷脂酶介导的磷脂水解及其对米糠储存期间三酰甘油 (TAG) 稳定性的影响的示意图。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/genome-editing-of-phospholipase-b-loc_os11g43510-promotes-rice-bran-triacylglycerol-stability-without-affecting-seed-germination2.jpg" /&